            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Thankfully, this isn’t yet another LS-swap car. In fact, the factory-original Flathead V8 is still installed. It’s been modified with Offenhauser aluminum heads, Edelbrock dual intake manifold, two Stromberg 2-bbl carbs, headers, and Smithy’s steel pack mufflers. To top off that setup, a 3-speed manual transmission is bolted up, promising plenty of fun on the street.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
